50|$|Each {{provincial council}} has elected one council member {{to serve in}} the Jirga (34 members), also each {{district}} council (34 members). Representatives of provincial councils will serve a term of four years, while representatives of district councils will serve a term of three years. Sebghatulla Mojadeddi was appointed President of <b>Meshrano</b> <b>Jirga.</b>|$|E
